item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

[quote=“reyx7, post:12, topic:367312”][quote author=the wanderer link=topic=463488.msg3391784#msg3391784 date=1289003456]

Try editing a little more, rather than the colors alone. maybe add some spikes, of your OWN wings, that way it has a personal touch. Also, good job on proper credits.

I actually once thought of redoing the over used wings. I don’t really like the concept enough though.

If I had a scanner I would show you multiple concepts I’ve drawn, they actually look pretty good.

Take a picture with you cell phone and send a picture message to your email. That’s what I do.
[/quote]
Ball in my blackberry fell out, I can’t scroll and I’ve learned to use other buttons, but the only thing I can do is txt. How much does a decent scanner cost?[/quote]
That is why blackberries suck, the ball is EASILY removable. Not the case in my phone, as the case has to come apart for it to be removed.

I know I will get flamed for the link, but its first thing that came up on google
